text: 14 Oct 2023. First time here and surprised by the taste of the food. We only ordered spicy fish and very fresh. The waiter or boss that served us was very friendly. In the restaurant got Karaoke set and I sang few songs ( OK la, many songs). Nice place to visit again.
Paper wrapped spicy fish is good. Big portion taste good. Reasonable price. Can choose aircon indoor or fresh air outdoor. Karaoke is foc, service crew very attentive.
Decent breakfast, staff service is very good! Singapore Laksa was a little too sour for me, if they would play down the sourness, i think it would be quite good!

Average food taste
Affordable price
Excellent service, the waiter is very attentive
The restaurant is decorated to China theme
A good place for eating and plenty of parking spaces.
